➜一份勾魂夺魄龙胆鱼、一锅干柴烈火鲍鱼鸡，让我深夜三点睡不着
http://www.sohu.com/a/415579578_110539	5023
<p>如题，许久未失眠了，“罪魁祸首”竟是今晚的勾魂夺魄龙胆鱼和干柴烈火鲍鱼鸡！</p>
<p>这两锅尤物同时在鹭鲜生美味分享馆出现，过瘾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200830/ba90b85ac71c425599775c68da7ea809.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200830/bfc7fbad6d2843c0895018f864c8724d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200830/e66a3215ec0a4d2cb48bbee79f93af6f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
